": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974836_1943374956076360_2484593514118294358_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=8nKa8_-MD-oQ7kNvgGOOtar&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBR69JkErOtQb2sXAiMeyTnH2jXFOaM5DULwxq5ietVPw&oe=676E9F82"}, {"file_name": "1.png", "id": "445060168517426", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75462964_445060171850759_5520915542327767111_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=MS8ArDhSiNEQ7kNvgGmcFac&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAUwAoXMb-b0zhc8AjG_8cZn0l2vaQ6Fgaz6J1ozOaK3g&oe=676E8C04"}, {"file_name": "5.png", "id": "467916352871409", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003282_467916356204742_1871921057092171900_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=aZ1p1D96z-EQ7kNvgGdHLGx&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD2fwDweLybS3nXshgz14G3LWwNJdpCYoUtt9DRaZ-k_A&oe=676EA8E2"}, {"file_name": "3.png", "id": "1934382610375855", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974473_1934382613709188_7156337812617042679_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=kR2lXPJNa4gQ7kNvgFFv-wv&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAF1u0f7J166GP0sDHGzUShw3FiDNYaWbM2JpREAgcpRQ&oe=676E92F3"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "landscape.png", "id": "1524760081483769", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974531_1524760084817102_6497712644828891067_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=WxI3odCdpNUQ7kNvgFxL8ub&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA4FB9ppeH2lAGz96UbsaHZJTHd5T8MKaiCWHFB5zqG4Q&oe=676E91EF"}, "display_name": "Mystery Box VR: Hidden Secrets", "keywords": [], "long_description": " AN IMMERSIVE VR PUZZLE EXPERIENCE\nInteract with objects, handles, buttons, and wheels on each side. Crack enigmas and collect hidden puzzle tiles on a random side of the boxes.\n\nYou won't be able to compare reality with fiction.\n\n# DISCOVER INVENTIONS\nOnce you unlock all 8 boxes of a Level Pack, you can compose a puzzle and discover a brief history of an invention.\n\nIt's not always easy to escape the room, so use all your IQ to crack the riddles. There's a logic behind all of them, even where it seems it's not!\n\n# IMMERSIVE SOUNDTRACK\nPlay the game with your headphones to get immersed in this amazing adventure.\n\n# HINTS\nGot stuck on some enigma? No worries, you can still get a helpful hint! You can also get in touch with me in case you really can't make it through a riddle, I'll be glad to help ;)\n\n# MULTILANGUAGE\nAvailable in English, French, Italian, German, Spanish, Russian, and Japanese.\n\nThe game language will change automatically based on the language settings of your device", "short_description": "A VR escape room game where you have to solve intriguing riddles to open boxes and discover nice stories about popular inventions!"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "$R36BSY5.png", "id": "3678762505771822", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031430_3678762509105155_2151975047074617165_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=y_iaIAWgr0wQ7kNvgHz-Eso&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBfE0jfSTFxX5elii96r_4rlu50EK4K_ipcmNTAE8nGEQ&oe=676E8DE5"}, {"file_name": "$R81V725.png", "id": "2720695481426567", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75262743_2720695484759900_604086922326600035_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=j-hS5ssbrb0Q7kNvgEcHsRW&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYChpGW-qzIrh5JnR3zz6n_AKtS9Laa-6V18v1B8veTBpA&oe=676E8CCD"}, {"file_name": "$RQ3SN6U.png", "id": "1552311425628973", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982519_1552311428962306_1218130395049083834_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6